{"tid":1822933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人間有情】何鴻燊病危，員工自願減薪幫老細渡難關！","createTime":"2020-01-13T09:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T14:38:48.000Z","uid":202464,"like":114,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"7b857e0a50ccf833f4a4062c2ab7e820ee5bed92","tid":1822933,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:18:15.000Z","msg":"信德（242）旗下噴射飛航要求員工減薪！<br />\n<br />\n有人報料指，噴射飛航向於本月10日向員工提出減薪方案，要求員工同意減薪：<br />\n<br />\n月薪一至三萬元減薪8%；<br />\n三萬至七萬元減薪10%；<br />\n七萬元以上減薪12%，<br />\n<br />\n並要求員工於16號之前簽同意書，否則將視作離職。"},{"pid":"0ef9f7147a72b78b6fbec9120fe5917a2f16d15e","tid":1822933,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ac1227e9d18638f5c8ca1de2ab63b8c71841db","tid":1822933,"uid":130365,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"會多d幫襯turbojet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3cbcd07bd8e543e22d6c357eb0e23200bc3cae","tid":1822933,"uid":198900,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"情你老母 唔夠陰屍紙洗？"},{"pid":"97857faae8775dabcd152c53aeda62e8d4e46258","tid":1822933,"uid":202464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a6ac1227e9d18638f5c8ca1de2ab63b8c71841db","tid":1822933,"uid":130365,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"會多d幫襯turbojet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"前線好多黃？"},{"pid":"e4552064efd10391bd185efe03ece442693d5538","tid":1822933,"uid":5737,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢死唔死關我員工撚事<br />\n死同好返 家產<br />\n員工又唔係有得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463fed39d9a4bdeb812f789925b9b9fd043fc3fc","tid":1822933,"uid":112622,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6000aa006ac51e90abb06a634c66d099f16d4cfe","tid":1822933,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"何超瓊做老細？"},{"pid":"c480f4b3466b5e8fdb3f98eed4ed48b9fd21731b","tid":1822933,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"減咁多?"},{"pid":"5b8ce75f9f7b223024f0c39c40515694f5bf1fa3","tid":1822933,"uid":76674,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"何家身家何家分"},{"pid":"9190527041197d27f018b1166eda6524432f0559","tid":1822933,"uid":261415,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"去澳門又被政治審查，分分鐘比人送中，咁危險香港人唔去都正常，怪得邊個，佢個女聯合國咁撚落力奶共，早登極落未好囉，做咁多衰野唔洗還啊。叫埋個女陪你囉，落地獄繼續奶共。"},{"pid":"aeff1f11695dbe39c481252c60244a0d1e3a676b","tid":1822933,"uid":202464,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"463fed39d9a4bdeb812f789925b9b9fd043fc3fc","tid":1822933,"uid":112622,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"惟一幸免的是月薪最低的基層員工，月薪1萬港元或以下薪金毋須調整。該公司於本月10日及13日分別於香港及澳門舉行簡介會宣布減薪通知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有員工表示，公司不但未與員工共度時艱，面對下滑經濟就胡亂減薪，完全不顧及為公司打拚多年的員工感受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據工聯會了解「話就話1萬蚊嗰啲唔使減，但幾乎無乜人的月薪仲係1萬」<br />\n<br />\n他指該公司去年第四季起，已要求員工每月至少放3日無薪假，現又減人工，且減幅驚人。"},{"pid":"7701242f05b3ea02f9f3d60158806ae67c04ebd4","tid":1822933,"uid":99493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"班員工做慣slave<br />\n知唔知老闆身家幾多<br />\n年年賺幾多億"},{"pid":"74a350e58e74326df33b67eef4fde62c38a3454f","tid":1822933,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e4552064efd10391bd185efe03ece442693d5538","tid":1822933,"uid":5737,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"rep